definitions: constructed, arranged, or marked like a net or network

examples.text: a pinafore of a finely reticulated pattern

shortDefinitions: constructed, arranged, or marked like net or network

definitions: (of porcelain) having a pattern of interlacing lines, especially of pierced work, forming a net or web.
shortDefinitions: (of porcelain) having pattern of interlacing lines forming net or web

definitions: relating to or denoting a style of decorated tracery characterized by circular shapes drawn at top and bottom into ogees, resulting in a netlike framework.
shortDefinitions: relating to style of tracery characterized by circular shapes
